hcc_text: East 138th Street is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top 10% for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in the Bronx)
info: At East 138th Street at Major Deegan Exwy Sb Exit 3, Madison Avenue Br Appr and Exterior Street, there were 5 severe injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
